ygData.messageBody:
Fanarian, when i read that u are a level 30 druid
and you still have leather armor my mouth fell wide
open. U at least have a Split paw vest don't u? Or
maybe a Lockjaw vest? I got all the spilt paw armor
before lvl 12, and i got a Lockjaw vest at lvl 14. My
druid as if of right now is lvl 16, 1/2 of a bbl to 17.
Maybe u consider these leather, but i don't. Also u
said that u have alot of Wis items. Tell me, what can
i get that is for 200pp or under for wis items. I
have goo ring and bracers. Also i traded a PBB(given
to me for free) for 2 bracers that were +10HP +10
manna each. was this a good deal, or did i get riped
off.
